er wavelengths, thus\nindicating that transmission loss well below the SRSL in the visible is\npossible with a surface roughness reduction and would open the possibility of\nthe first UV low-loss light- guidance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2016 16:37:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-06"}
