uum-single-mode squeezed states (characterized by a given\nbandwidth and frequency). Time-averaging is required for the squeezed case,\nshowing both results in a unified way. For the thermal state, all the\nwell-known equilibrium results can be successfully reproduced. Finally, we\ncompared the initial conditions' contribution and the total force for each\ncase, showing that the latter can be tuned in a wide range of values through\nvarying the size of the bandwidth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2016 18:23:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-18"}
