inally, key results on the use of cognitive\nhierarchy theory in the IoT are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2016 19:43:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2016 17:45:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-14"}
