ting BH merger rates lies in\nthe potentially wide variety of galaxy host systems, with different degrees of\ngas dissipation and heating, yielding decay timescales from ~10 to ~300 Myr.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2016 20:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Feb 2017 15:49:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-29"}
